race.comment: POSSIBILITIES (5) has been consistent without winning hitting the top-four at her past eight starts and strikes a very winnable contest here. Only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be playing a major role in the outcome. KOBABILITY (14) has been right there in all five runs this preparation including placing twice around this circuit. Should be right there when the whips are cracking. BLACKJACK (21) strips fitter second-up from the break and gets the services of Rodd in the irons. Include in calculations. GUNNIE GUNFIGHTER (1) has finished runner-up at his past couple here and looks to be building up to a maiden victory. In the mix. RED SAMOVAR (15) next best from the Vandyke yard.
